releases.name: v0.5.0
releases.body:
## New Redux DevTools features (https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/pull/16)
- Pausing and locking (See [redux-devtools-extension v2.7.0](https://github.com/zalmoxisus/redux-devtools-extension/releases/tag/v2.7.0))
- Better time travelling with changes right in the Graph Monitor (See [redux-devtools-extension v2.8.0](https://github.com/zalmoxisus/redux-devtools-extension/releases/tag/v2.8.0))
- Print the graph view of the app state or the changes log (See [redux-devtools-extension v2.8.1](https://github.com/zalmoxisus/redux-devtools-extension/releases/tag/v2.8.1)) (**NOTE** It's doesn't have preview on Electron)
- ......

## New Redux enhancer / compose API

Refer to [redux-devtools-extension](https://github.com/zalmoxisus/redux-devtools-extension/releases/tag/v2.7.0), we provide a new way instead of `reduxNativeDevTools` and `reduxNativeDevTools.updateStore`:
- `window.__REDUX_DEVTOOLS_EXTENSION__` (alias `reduxNativeDevTools`)
- `window.__REDUX_DEVTOOLS_EXTENSION_COMPOSE__` (alias `reduxNativeDevToolsCompose`)

``` js
const composeEnhancers = window.__REDUX_DEVTOOLS_EXTENSION_COMPOSE__ ?
  window.__REDUX_DEVTOOLS_EXTENSION_COMPOSE__({
    /* options */
  }) :
  compose;
const enhancer = composeEnhancers(
  applyMiddleware(...middlewares)
);
```

See [README.md](https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger#redux-devtools) for more information.

## Multi-store support

Now we can use the redux enhancer for each store, and we can switch instances on monitor:

![2016-11-03 7 47 25](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3001525/19964726/6bee9bf4-a1fe-11e6-849b-fee363ee032b.png)

## Other changes
- React Developer Tools commit is now [bacc514a31f1b78f34c2761e9d0910ec3264b496](https://github.com/jhen0409/react-devtools/commit/bacc514a31f1b78f34c2761e9d0910ec3264b496)
- Persist app state https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/e036eaf8d901a8da85c25b556b9195b9973dfb6c https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/0de1409574a00e22b055504040ba11e5b8755cf7
- Auto update support for macOS https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/262a86c99dfaa8d0bdffcb9d591f1c2fc0287e96
- `Check for Updates...` on menu https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/560c7f37a5c76b14e68805f90424813fdd59491e
- Rename `RNDebuggerWorker.js` from `debugger.worker.js` (improve contexts name of console tab) https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/e2af22f88b27f2eaaec8ee5472189142d950b50e
- Shortcuts for Linux / Windows https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/2067f51e2c6a768a5a84aef4c6b2e289eec43cd4
- Update debugger worker from upstream https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/69a73b723a6f86e5e5a20d963d7eabb15b692426
- Optimize https://github.com/jhen0409/react-native-debugger/commit/b3dbd69de89772c6c9248ecd11f8fcc37e95647e
